name: Jack Howell
description: I’m a calm, passionate, understanding person. I am always trying to give a chance to someone to show her inner world, her attitude to me, open her thoughts, dreams, and desires. I am a good listener, but also ready to give advice and help to close and near people. I think that people are different, but kind from the very beginning, just some circumstances of their lives make them to act not always honest.
